<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM1.10.10">
<l>maṟappu ñāṉamu nāṉoṉ ṟuṇarntilaṉ</l>
<l>maṟakku meṉṟucen tāmaraik kaṇṇoṭu</l>
<l>maṟappaṟa veṉṉuḷḷē maṉṉiṉāṉ ṟaṉṉai</l>
<l>maṟappa ṉōviṉi yāṉeṉ maṇiyaiyē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Both forgetting and knowledge I do not understand at all.</l>
<l>Thinking “he will forget, with red lotus eyes,</l>
<l>the one who dwells in my mind so that forgetting is cut off,</l>
<l>will I forget now my sapphire?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
